VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ── IPv6 checklist ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Enable IPv6 in Supabase Dashboard → Settings → Database → Enable IPv6
# 2. Your router/ISP must support IPv6 (if you're reading this you already do)
# 3. Vite dev server already binds to '::' (all IPv6 interfaces) in vite.config.ts
# No further code changes needed.
